title: England's lower clubs enjoy spotlight after virus fears shut down top leagues
description: HALIFAX/DARTFORD, England: England's Premier League and 72-team Football League closed down on Saturday due to concerns over the coronavirus but clubs in the fifth tier and below defiantly took to the field - to the delight of football addicts across the coun…
